        </p>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-pink-600 mb-4">Step 4: Chrome Lips</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Line lips with a grey or black pencil, fill in with metallic silver lipstick, and top with a chrome-effect gloss or pigment. For a subtle look, dab silver highlight just at the center of the lips.
        </p>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-pink-600 mb-4">Step 5: Final Touches</h4>
